    <searchtitle>Data Element: REFERRED TO SERVICE (SNOMED CT) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_referred_to_service__snomed_ct_">REFERRED TO SERVICE (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_clinical_terminology_code">CLINICAL TERMINOLOGY CODE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_referred_to_service__snomed_ct_">REFERRED TO SERVICE (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct">SNOMED CT</xref>
® concept ID which is used to identify the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
 to which a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 was referred for admission or opinion by the treating 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct_refset">SNOMED CT Refset</xref>
 Metadata:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct_refset">Refset</xref>
               <p>FSN: Emergency care referral procedures simple reference set (foundation metadata concept)</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct_refset">Refset</xref>
               <p>Id: 991451000000108</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further details relating to the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct_refset">SNOMED CT Refset</xref>
 Metadata, see the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_data_dictionary_for_care">Data Dictionary for Care</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_data_dictionary_for_care">DD4C</xref>) website at: 
              <xref href="https://dd4c.digital.nhs.uk/dd4c/publishedmetadatas/intid/721"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Emergency care referral procedures</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
